thread.title: Bryan C.

author: Bryan C.
title: Bryan C.
text: I absolutely love Onnit, but their prices are out of my range on many items. Alpha Brain is a wonderful supplement that truly works. I ordered a baseball hat during my last order, and the bill was bent pretty badly. The box used was too small, I believe. I'll have to send my first item back, hopefully the process will be smooth. Onnit, I love what you're trying to do, but please get those prices down if you can!
